{"data":[{"date":"07:07 05/08","title":"Leonardo Bonucci quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/leonardo-bonucci-khong-xin-loi-sau-khi-tro-lai-juventus.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Leonardo Bonucci tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i khi v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Juventus sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian phi\u00eau b\u1ea1t sang AC Milan, m\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bonucci tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan, Leonardo Bonucci \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Mattia Caldara t\u1edbi Rossoneri. H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Bonucci \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00e3i nhau v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Leonardo Bonucci kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Leonardo Bonucci kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/leonardo-bonucci-khong-xin-loi-sau-khi-tro-lai-juventus.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Leonardo Bonucci kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Bonucci, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 hay nh\u1ea5t Italia th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Juventus, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, gi\u01a1 l\u00ean nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Bonucci ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i c\u00f4ng khai v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1eddi b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Juventus cho r\u1eb1ng Bonucci s\u1edf d\u0129 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus l\u00e0 do AC Milan hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng. C\u1ef1u Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch ng\u01b0\u1eddi Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Li Yonghong \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t AC Milan v\u00e0o tay Elliott Management - Qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Hoa K\u1ef3 do kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e3 vay \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V, Leonardo Bonucci kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i: \"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bonucci tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00e8 2017 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea3y n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Juventus, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 19 b\u00e0n sau 319 tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ebfc m\u00f3c Dybala trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hai hi\u1ec7p trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2016-17 g\u1eb7p Real Madrid d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Bonucci, Juventus m\u00f9a n\u00e0y c\u00f2n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam 4 t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1c g\u1ed3m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Mattia Perin, Emre Can, Joao Cancelo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Leonardo Bonucci:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league-176-193654.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: T\u00e1i h\u1ee3p \u201cc\u1eebu \u0111en\u201d, Juventus kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi-176-192614.html\">Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus: \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-va-ac-milan-sap-trao-doi-bom-tan-176-191928.html\">Juventus v\u00e0 AC Milan s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hlv-gattuso-muon-bonucci-o-lai-milan-176-191897.html\">HLV Milan n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sang M.U ho\u1eb7c Real?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-don-dau-vu-bonucci-172-191595.html\">MU nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Italia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/psg-mu-va-chelsea-dai-chien-vi-bonucci-172-191094.html\">PSG, MU v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao kh\u1ee7ng AC Milan</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nN.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5099","checkdouble":"193737"},{"date":"07:18 05/08","title":"Ancelotti b\u1ecf h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/ancelotti-bo-hop-bao-sau-tham-bai-truoc-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb The Kop h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 0-5, HLV Ancelotti chia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng tham gia cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o.\r\n</h2><h2>Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Napoli b\u1ecf h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1ea1ng, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Napoli th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. H\u1ecd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng s\u1eadp b\u1eaby ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool, v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n thua. Sau tr\u1eadn, Ancelotti \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Napoli ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o v\u00ec m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n&rdquo; &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, &ldquo;b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch. Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ancelotti l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Sky Sports, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n n\u00e0y, HLV Italia \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0m phi\u1ec1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ancelotti chia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool 0-5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ancelotti chia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool 0-5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/ance.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Ancelotti chia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Napoli \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1edfi m\u1edf, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u00e0ng trai \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 theo k\u1ecbp h\u1ecd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 b\u1ecb tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng &ndash; v\u0169 kh\u00ed m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Napoli kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Carlo Ancelotti chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Napoli s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu n\u1eefa v\u1edbi Dortmund v\u00e0 Wolfsburg, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Lazio v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 18/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Liverpool-vs-Napoli.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-ra-mat-thanh-cong-klopp-noi-gi-172-193744.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/alisson-ra-mat-thanh-cong-klopp-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-ra-mat-thanh-cong-klopp-noi-gi-172-193744.html\">Alisson ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Napoli, HLV Jurgen Klopp h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Alisson &ndash; bom t\u1ea5n 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-50-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193740.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/video-tong-hop-liverpool-50-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-50-napoli-giao-huu-clb-he-2018-329-193740.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Liverpool 5-0 Napoli (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5098","checkdouble":"193747"},{"date":"07:50 05/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 05/8): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay 5/8, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi BHL c\u00f9ng HLV Park Hang Seo.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman t\u1ed1i nay, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c,\u2026 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea1ng danh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay hay l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng. 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ai \u0111i, ai \u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 058) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 058) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Nhan-dinh-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman-(19h30,-ngay-058)-Co-hoi-cho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1eadn\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c 'k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5' tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, anh ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o SLNA, s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n.\u00a0Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ecfng \u0111o\u00e1n b\u1edfi th\u1ea7y Park lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea5u Oman, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng\u00a0bi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0u \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng pha kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i U23 c\u1ee7a hai n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (tham d\u1ef1 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 \u0110TQG) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p \u0110TQG Oman \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m, trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2004. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111i v\u00e0 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 0-6 v\u00e0 0-2. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Oman v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a 14 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc, khi ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u00c1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Do \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin, b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh v\u00e0 khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-da-lo-ra-nhung-van-de-dac-biet-o-he-thong-phong-thu-168-193719.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/u23-viet-nam-da-lo-ra-nhung-van-de-dac-biet-o-he-thong-phong-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-da-lo-ra-nhung-van-de-dac-biet-o-he-thong-phong-thu-168-193719.html\">\u201cU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7\u201d</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine, HLV k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh cho r\u1eb1ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0o?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, U23 Oman \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 U23 Uzbekistan trong cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. Do \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Oman trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh khi gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran 2-0 v\u00e0 5-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kyrgyzstan (ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1). Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u00ec (3-2), Jordan (2-1) v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Cameroon v\u00e0 2-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3i qua 90 ph\u00fat kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh v\u1eeba tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, tr\u00e1nh l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i, song \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Trung \u0110\u00f4ng lu\u00f4n m\u1ea1nh \u1edf l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 058) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 058) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Nhan-dinh-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman-(19h30,-ngay-058)-Co-hoi-cho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2 t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. B\u1ed9 ba trung v\u1ec7 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. Trong s\u1ed1 5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 V\u0103n Thanh (ph\u1ea3i), V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 V\u0103n H\u1eadu (tr\u00e1i). Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Oman c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Palestine. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 nh\u1eb1m th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park. B\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Mr. Park s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 cho t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft, nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9, th\u1ee9c \u0103n. V\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 NHM.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa\u00a0<o:p></o:p>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0 Palestine s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 16h30. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam-168-193695.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam-168-193695.html\">B\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, HLV Uzbekistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman,  HLV \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-giao-huu-u23-viet-nam-21-u23-palestine-292-193665.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-1 U23 Palestine</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i c\u00fap T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam:\u00a0Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; Duy M\u1ea1nh, T\u1ea5n Sinh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Ti\u1ebfn Linh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Oman:\u00a0Mukhaini; Harthi, Rashi Al, Shayadi, Sulaman Al, Balushi, Mubarak Al, Saleh Al, Al Hidi, Ali Al, Al Sabhi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n: 2-2.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5097","checkdouble":"193749"},{"date":"08:39 05/08","title":"L\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u2013 Oman: B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u00f2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman. V\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u01a1n l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tung ra s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/nhom-du-bi-tap-rieng-tien-dung-gan-nhu-mat-suat-bat-chinh-vao-tay-van-lam.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung g\u1ed7 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng. Ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, song l\u00fac n\u00e0y anh \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. V\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Thanh H\u00f3a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. B\u1ed9 ba ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u00eda tr\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, Hu\u1ef3nh T\u1ea5n Sinh v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean: L\u00ea V\u0103n S\u01a1n, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng g\u1ed3m V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn Linh. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, HLV Park Hang-seo c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi trao t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo \u2018x\u1edbi tung\u2019 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i b\u1edfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn l\u1ecdc v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra b\u1ed9 khung thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u qua t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U23 Palestine \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c cho ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eb9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u00eam Oman. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cao.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 05/8): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br />\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay 5/8, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5096","checkdouble":"193753"},{"date":"08:58 05/08","title":"\u201cU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 an to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/3/u23-viet-nam-se-da-an-toan-truoc-oman.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman.</h2><h2>&ldquo;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 an to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai g\u1eb7p U23 Oman. V\u1ec1 \u00fd thuy\u1ebft, Oman kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n Palestine hay Iraq, Qatar,&hellip; nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u trong n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh cho r\u1eb1ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Oman t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 an to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 an to\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/HLV-Nguyen-Thanh-Vinh-U23-Viet-Nam-se-da-an-toan-truoc-Oman-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T&nbsp;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB SLNA chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o D\u00e2n Tr\u00ed: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Oman c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng hay nh\u01b0 Palestine, b\u1edfi Oman b\u1ecb Uzbekistan \u00e9p s\u00e2n to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd gi\u1ea5u b\u00e0i v\u00e0 gi\u1ea5u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, b\u1edfi theo h\u00ecnh dung c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, Oman kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Oman n\u00f3i chung mang phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c khu v\u1ef1c Trung \u0110\u00f4ng, c\u0169ng nhanh, m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 kh\u00e9o. N\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i, v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f9ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 v\u1eabn h\u01a1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.&nbsp;Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 coi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1c chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1c th\u1eafng, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd thi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m tung h\u1ebft b\u00e0i cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m. L\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 an to\u00e0n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; Oman s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t, tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u00f4ng Park s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1eadn Uzbekistan vs Palestine s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h30 c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan-168-193753.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-viet-nam-oman-bui-tien-dung-bat-chinh-minh-vuong-giu-bang-thu-quan-168-193753.html\">L\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; Oman: B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n?</span><br>\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u00f2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-193749.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman (19h30, ng\u00e0y 05/8): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i nay 5/8, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5095","checkdouble":"193755"},{"date":"07:32 05/08","title":"Inter quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luka Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/inter-quyet-tam-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-luka-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Inter chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Modric v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin, r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phi v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nInter \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi sao Real<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, Luka Modric ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 &ndash; khi gi\u00fap \u0110T Croatia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Inter.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup di\u1ec5n ra. Anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 no n\u00ea danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Modric v\u1eabn li\u00ean h\u1ec7 m\u1eadt thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n chuy\u1ec3n sang Inter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Inter chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Modric v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Inter chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Modric v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-257-MU-tong-tan-cong-Willian-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Inter chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Modric v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00eda CLB Italia c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Spalleti chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Luka Modric s\u1ebd quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 CLB n\u00e0o. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00ean \u1ed5n. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Inter, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Inter chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Modric, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 750 tri\u1ec7u euro &ndash; s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia quy\u1ebft ch\u00ed ra \u0111i, Real Madrid s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/la-thu-cam-dong-cua-tien-ve-modric-gui-dap-co-be-5-tuoi-bi-ung-thu-188-192078.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/la-thu-cam-dong-cua-tien-ve-modric-gui-dap-co-be-5-tuoi-bi-ung-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/la-thu-cam-dong-cua-tien-ve-modric-gui-dap-co-be-5-tuoi-bi-ung-thu-188-192078.html\">L\u00e1 th\u01b0 c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric g\u1eedi \u0111\u00e1p c\u00f4 b\u00e9 5 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb ung th\u01b0</span><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i l\u00e1 th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a fan nh\u00ed.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/thuoc-phim-hiem-ve-cau-be-luka-modric-5-tuoi-chan-cuu-giua-bay-soi-188-191375.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/thuoc-phim-hiem-ve-cau-be-luka-modric-5-tuoi-chan-cuu-giua-bay-soi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/hau-truong/thuoc-phim-hiem-ve-cau-be-luka-modric-5-tuoi-chan-cuu-giua-bay-soi-188-191375.html\">Th\u01b0\u1edbc phim hi\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu b\u00e9 Luka Modric 5 tu\u1ed5i ch\u0103n c\u1eebu gi\u1eefa b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u1edbc phim t\u01b0 li\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Pavle Balenovic c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 29 n\u0103m ghi l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Croatia, n\u01a1i Luka Modric \u0111ang ph\u1ee5 gi\u00fap gia \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u0103n c\u1eebu gi\u1eefa b\u1ea7y s\u00f3i hoang d\u00e3.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5094","checkdouble":"193748"},{"date":"07:37 05/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City (Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh, 21h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8): Ra ng\u00f5 g\u1eb7p n\u00fai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-21h00-ngay-58-ra-ngo-gap-nui.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia tay Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tho\u00e1t d\u1edbp Juventus \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 \u00dd, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng CLB m\u1edbi.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi m\u1ebb v\u00e0 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1ed1i nay v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh Community Shield gi\u1eefa hai nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 FA Cup.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u1edf Wembley l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa Chelsea vs Man City, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00edch c\u1ef1c hay ho nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn, x\u00e9t tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc &ldquo;qu\u00e2n xanh&rdquo; Perth Glory n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dac, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ecb Inter Milan c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Arsenal c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a v\u00e0 d\u1eabn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1eafng thua tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, Man City th\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n khi thua tr\u1eafng hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean g\u1eb7p Dortmund v\u00e0 Liverpool, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng g\u1ee1 g\u1ea1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Bayern Munich v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m, c\u1ecd s\u00e1t nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y c\u00f3 bao gi\u1edd mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t Man City tr\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Chelsea v\u00e0 n\u1eb1m c\u1eeda tr\u00ean \u1edf Wembley.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u00fd do d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-yeu-lai-tu-dau-voi-433-cua-sarriball-172-193710.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/goc-chelsea-yeu-lai-tu-dau-voi-433-cua-sarriball.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-chelsea-yeu-lai-tu-dau-voi-433-cua-sarriball-172-193710.html\">G\u00f3c Chelsea: Y\u00eau l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi 4-3-3 c\u1ee7a Sarriball</span><br>\r\nT\u1eeb h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ba h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Antonio Conte \u0111\u1ebfn s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4-3-3 c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri, tri\u1ebft l\u00fd v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch n\u01a1i Chelsea s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t t\u1eeb...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 ba Pep Guardiola l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u0129nh h\u1ed9i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng, v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t nh\u1ea5t, Maurizio Sarri v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh thu\u1ea7n th\u1ee5c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd ph\u1ea3ng ph\u1ea5t qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7. C\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho Sarri khi trong tay \u00f4ng hi\u1ec7n th\u1eddi thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nh\u1eefng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Jorginho k\u00e9o sang c\u00f9ng t\u1eeb Napoli.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City (Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh, 21h00 ng\u00e0y 58) Ra ng\u00f5 g\u1eb7p n\u00fai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City (Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh, 21h00 ng\u00e0y 58) Ra ng\u00f5 g\u1eb7p n\u00fai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Nhan-dinh-Chelsea-vs-Man-City-(Sieu-Cup-Anh,-21h00-ngay-58)-Ra-ngo-gap-nui-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng g\u00e2y nh\u1ee9c nh\u1ed1i cho c\u1ea3 Chelsea c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Man City, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n h\u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ch\u01b0a tham gia b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o, nh\u1eefng Hazard, Giroud, Willian, Kante, Courtois hay De Bruyne, Sterling, Fernandinho, Stones v\u00e0 Ederson c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 sung m\u00e3n v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u1edd c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1. D\u00f9 sao, Sarri c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap n\u00e0y h\u01a1n Guardiola cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea7u xu\u00f4i \u0111u\u00f4i l\u1ecdt trong ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n. 59 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t ch\u01b0a gi\u00e0nh b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c HLV d\u1eabn d\u1eaft nh\u1eefng CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 e r\u1eb1ng l\u1ef1c b\u1ea5t t\u00f2ng t\u00e2m cho c\u1ef1u nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng n\u00e0y khi chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man City v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u1edbi ti\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u00e0n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Riyad Mahrez.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City (Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh, 21h00 ng\u00e0y 58) Ra ng\u00f5 g\u1eb7p n\u00fai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City (Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh, 21h00 ng\u00e0y 58) Ra ng\u00f5 g\u1eb7p n\u00fai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Nhan-dinh-Chelsea-vs-Man-City-(Sieu-Cup-Anh,-21h00-ngay-58)-Ra-ngo-gap-nui-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Guardiola \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch l\u00e0nh \u00edt d\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf v\u00f2ng khai m\u1ea1c Premier League 2018/19 cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n sau.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1edbi Sarri ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u khi \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd&hellip; c\u1ea7n thua, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn to\u00e0n c\u1ee5c m\u1ecdi y\u1ebfu khuy\u1ebft c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ecdng \u1edf Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ea5p r\u00fat ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda s\u1edbm \u1edf Anh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi ma l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb Real Madrid, qua \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 FA Cup nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p x\u1ea5u nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb gi\u1edd cho \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y 9/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chelsea (4-3-3): 1. Caballero; 28. Azpilicueta &ndash; 30. Luiz &ndash; 2. Ruidger &ndash; 3. Alonso; 4. Fabregas &ndash; 5. Jorginho &ndash; 8. Barkley; 11. Pedro &ndash; 29. Morata &ndash; 20. Hudson-Odoi<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man City (4-3-3): 1. Bravo; 50. Bolton &ndash; 50. Garcia &ndash; 14. Laporte &ndash; 35. Zinchenko; 20. Bernando &ndash; 8. Gundogan &ndash; 47. Foden; 26. Mahrez &ndash; 10. Aguero &ndash; 19. Sane<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh 2018: 1-3<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5093","checkdouble":"193739"},{"date":"07:03 05/08","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a M.U b\u1ecb ch\u00ea kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-bi-che-khong-biet-phong-ngu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadn k\u1ec1, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Valverde l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00ea bai Yerry Mina tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u00e1n anh ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nBarca kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 Mina<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Barca. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd, khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Clement Lenglet. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Barca \u0111ang c\u00f3 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Pique, Umtiti v\u00e0 Lenglet, trong khi Mina, Vermaelen v\u00e0 Malon Santos n\u1eb1m trong di\u1ec7n nguy hi\u1ec3m. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Vermaelen s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a Mina s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1n g\u00f3i ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1ed9t nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Barca l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 su\u1ea5t cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, v\u1edbi t\u00e2n binh Arturo Vidal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, PCT c\u1ee7a Barca &ndash; Jordi Mestre l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng: &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 (v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c M.U h\u1ecfi mua Mina). Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng b\u1edfi Yerry Mina m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 HLV.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Valverde l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00ea bai Yerry Mina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Valverde l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00ea bai Yerry Mina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/ngay-hom-nay-38.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Valverde l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00ea bai Yerry Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Ernesto Valverde chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Yerry l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Yerry, v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf t\u1ea1i \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Valverde l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u00ea bai Yerry Mina.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao Colombia. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd nh\u1eadn tin, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/yerry-mina-chia-se-su-that-thu-vi-ve-messi-180-192363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/11/yerry-mina-chia-se-su-that-thu-vi-ve-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/yerry-mina-chia-se-su-that-thu-vi-ve-messi-180-192363.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a M.U chia s\u1ebb s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 Messi</span><br>\r\nGi\u1eefa tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c, trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Messi v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-mua-yerry-mina-172-192619.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/mu-muon-mua-yerry-mina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-mua-yerry-mina-172-192619.html\">Ch\u00ea Alderweireld v\u00e0 Maguire qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft, M.U ch\u1ed1t mua ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y</span><br>\r\nM.U mu\u1ed1n mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0a ra sau khi t\u1eeb b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Toby Alderweireld v\u00e0 Harry Maguire v\u00ec...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5092","checkdouble":"193745"},{"date":"08:04 05/08","title":"L\u00fd do n\u00e0o khi\u1ebfn Pep Guardiola tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1i?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/10/17/ly-do-nao-khien-pep-guardiola-tro-thanh-hlv-bat-kha-chien-bai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh si\u00eau c\u00fap v\u1edbi Chelsea, Pep Guardiola chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Man City l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPep chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">100 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Man xanh \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, khi h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9. V\u1edbi Pep Guardiola, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf v\u00ec sao m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 HLV h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 \u0103n may g\u1eb7p th\u1eddi.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng. Theo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng. N\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn s\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n, v\u00e0 khao kh\u00e1t gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ec3 thua kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 HLV n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh xa c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pep Guardiola chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/HLV-Pep-Guardiola-chia-se-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed9i l\u1ed7i. Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea1n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Pep ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 Community Shield, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng m\u1edbi cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u. Champions League, m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn s\u1ed1. M\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7, m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 s\u1ebd ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, Champions League l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Premier League&rdquo; &ndash; Pep chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-21h00-ngay-58-ra-ngo-gap-nui-172-193739.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-21h00-ngay-58-ra-ngo-gap-nui.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-21h00-ngay-58-ra-ngo-gap-nui-172-193739.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Man City (Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh, 21h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8): Ra ng\u00f5 g\u1eb7p n\u00fai</span><br>\r\nChia tay Napoli \u0111\u1ec3 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tho\u00e1t d\u1edbp Juventus \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 \u00dd, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u ngay...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city-172-193661.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city-172-193661.html\">3 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi d\u00e0nh cho Sarri tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap v\u1edbi Man City</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a The Blues d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ng\u1ed5n ngang nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1....</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5091","checkdouble":"193751"},{"date":"18:01 04/08","title":"Gattuso: \"Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/gattuso-chang-cau-thu-nao-co-the-tu-choi-chung-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Gennaro Gattuso chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Milan v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, sau khi m\u1edbi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 ng\u00f4i sao t\u1eeb Juventus.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMilan \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rossoneri d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 trao \u0111\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i v\u1edbi Juventus, khi chia tay trung v\u1ec7 Bonucci c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1p Gonzalo Higuain, c\u00f9ng ng\u00f4i sao gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng Caldara.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi v\u1ee5 trao \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y, HLV Gattuso c\u1ee7a Milan t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng: &ldquo;V\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Mattia Caldara l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi CLB, c\u00f2n Gonzalo Higuain t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 anh \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 \u1edf nh\u00e0, c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u00f9ng Milan. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Higuain r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 tin r\u1eb1ng, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Rossoneri.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gattuso chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Milan, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i\" title=\"Milan chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 2 t\u00e2n binh t\u1eeb Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/gattuso-chang-cau-thu-nao-co-the-tu-choi-chung-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gattuso chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Milan, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00ec l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00e0o h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Milan. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, hay n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Milan, ch\u1eb3ng ai n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh nh\u01b0 Higuain, Caldara v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu, t\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau c\u1ee7a CLB. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Milan bay cao tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi h\u1ebft l\u1eddi t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, Gattuso \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Vidal &ndash; c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ai l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch Vidal. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 anh \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Vidal khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn binh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Anh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Vidal. V\u00ec sao ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u01b0? C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a cLB, v\u00e0 lu\u1eadt C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh \u1ea5y&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Gattuso chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Milan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league-176-193654.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league-176-193654.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: T\u00e1i h\u1ee3p &ldquo;c\u1eebu \u0111en&rdquo;, Juventus kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf Champions League</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5, khi trung v\u1ec7 Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-gonzalo-higuain-toi-ac-milan-176-192568.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-gonzalo-higuain-toi-ac-milan.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-gonzalo-higuain-toi-ac-milan-176-192568.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn San...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi-176-192614.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi-176-192614.html\">Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus: \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i</span><br>\r\nLeonardo Bonucci tin r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 1 n\u0103m sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Milan.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5090","checkdouble":"193717"},{"date":"18:40 04/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U23 Uzbekistan sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/doi-hinh-u23-uzbekistan-sang-viet-nam-khong-chat-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra sau khi U23 Uzbekistan c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung \u00c1 sang H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1.</h2><h2>U23 Uzbekistan kh\u00f4ng mang 'h\u00e0ng x\u1ecbn' sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/2177242_105897.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Uzbekistan (tr\u1eafng) kh\u00f4ng mang nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uzbekistan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mang m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u1ec3 ra nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i\u00a0Odiljon Hamrobekov, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Jasurbek Yakhshiboev hay c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o cao k\u1ec1u Andrey Sidorov.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Uzbekistan sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1 m\u1edbi m\u1ebb. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 HLV\u00a0Ravshan Khaydarov, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Park Hang-seo \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft t\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 v\u00f4 danh\u00a0Nuraliev Dilshod.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1eeb ph\u00eda L\u0110B\u0110 Uzbekistan, \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Uzbekistan \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh l\u00e0m m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn\u00a0Olympic Tokyo 2020. Do \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu n\u00e0y, trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n U23 Uzbekistan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 th\u1ee7\u00a0th\u00e0nh Khamraev Dilshod, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Rustamov Oybek, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isroilov Abdujamol, Nurulloev Sukhrob.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u00e0n ph\u1ee5c th\u00f9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i 7/8 t\u1edbi.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam-168-193695.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bi-cam-hoa-ngay-ra-quan-hlv-uzbekistan-gui-loi-thach-thuc-toi-u23-viet-nam-168-193695.html\">B\u1ecb c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, HLV Uzbekistan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman,  HLV \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\">HLV Uzbekistan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-uzbekistan-the-hien-su-tu-tin-truoc-tran-tai-dau-viet-nam-168-192526.html\">U23 Uzbekistan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i ngay khi v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ebfn Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5089","checkdouble":"193718"},{"date":"18:40 04/08","title":"\u201cU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/3/u23-viet-nam-da-lo-ra-nhung-van-de-dac-biet-o-he-thong-phong-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine, HLV k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh cho r\u1eb1ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2.</h2><h2>HLV\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn\u00a0</span>Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-1 Palestine</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i t\u1ed1i 3/8 v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng 2-1 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2 khi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t r\u1eddi s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguyen Thanh Vinh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/3/28/u23-viet-nam-co-the-nhat-bang-i.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o D\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t, v\u1ecb c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Th\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cV\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong hi\u1ec7p 1. U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n 1 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vai tr\u00f2, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung, h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n em.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sang\u00a0hi\u1ec7p 2, khi HLV Park Hang Seo b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m th\u00eam v\u1ec1 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 ra nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu Palestine d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110T U23 Palestine cho r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Vinh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u00e0i to\u00e1n ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i: \u201cT\u00f4i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u00e8n gi\u0169a c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang-seo su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua c\u0169ng l\u00e0 pha b\u00f3ng hi\u1ebfm hoi ch\u00fang ta ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u th\u1ebf chi\u1ec1u cao khi b\u1eadt l\u00ean tranh ch\u1ea5p, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y mai 5/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi U23 Oman, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Palestine s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h./.\u00a0<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nHighlight Viet Nam vs Palestine</strong><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-hinh-u23-uzbekistan-sang-viet-nam-khong-chat-luong-168-193718.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/doi-hinh-u23-uzbekistan-sang-viet-nam-khong-chat-luong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-hinh-u23-uzbekistan-sang-viet-nam-khong-chat-luong-168-193718.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U23 Uzbekistan sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng?</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t ra sau khi U23 Uzbekistan c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung \u00c1 sang H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng g\u1ed3m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span><br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\"></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5088","checkdouble":"193719"},{"date":"21:57 04/08","title":"Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: PSG 4-0 Monaco (Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/video-tong-hop-psg-40-monaco-sieu-cup-phap-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Monaco thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, PSG d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0, qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111o\u1ea1t Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Monaco thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, PSG d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0, qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111o\u1ea1t Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng:<br>\r\nPSG: Di Mar\u00eda\u00a0 (33', 90+2'), Nkunku\u00a0 (40'), Weah\u00a0 (68')<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o, PSG v\u1eabn ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n Monaco, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Thiago Silva, Marco Verratti, Adrien Rabiot hay Angel Di Maria. S\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. PSG c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng 70%, tung ra 7 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn 2-0.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng PSG vs Monaco 4-0 Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng PSG vs Monaco 4-0 Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/di-maria-00.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDi Maria l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 33 v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u00f2n c\u00f3 2 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1o ra s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 40, Nkunku nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i N'Soki.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Monaco, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. \u0110\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ra ngo\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Rony Lopes trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly ch\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng ch\u1eebng 5m. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u, Tielemans b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c khi c\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u1eadp ng\u01b0\u1eddi Thiago Silva \u0111i ra ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, PSG ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 PSG c\u00f3 th\u00eam hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa, N'Soki ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u00f2n Di Maria c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 67 (Timothy Weah) v\u00e0 90 +2 (Di Maria). V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, PSG l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111o\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u:<br>\r\nPSG: Buffon; Dagba, Thiago Silva (Bernede 73'), Rimane, N'Soki; Verratti (Neymar 76'), Lass Diarra (Marquinhos 64'), Rabiot; Di Maria, Timothy Weah, Nkunku.<br>\r\nMonaco: Benaglio; Raggu, Glik, Jemerson, Julien Serrano; Aholou, Pele (Diop), Rony Lopes (Mboula 74'), Tielemans, Grandsir (Balde 46'); Jovetic.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5087","checkdouble":"193734"}]}